title: Evergreen Jazz Christmas
desc:
The Washington Heights Chamber Orchestra celebrates the holiday season with a free jazz Christmas concert featuring bassist Ike Sturm and his nine-piece ensemble, Evergreen. Soulful, lyrical, and downright joyful, Evergreen?s music will elevate your Holiday spirits.
